        {
            "title": "中國11月信貸擴張仍受限 貸款增速令人失望",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國11月信貸擴張速度較去年同期溫和回升，但貸款增速仍令人失望，凸顯出家庭和企業借貸疲軟仍然是拖累經濟的一大憂患。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博根據中國人民銀行周五公佈的數據計算顯示，11月廣義信貸衡量指標社會融資規模成長2.5萬億元人民幣。接受彭博調查的經濟學家預期中值為2.2萬億元，上年同期為2.3萬億元</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當月金融機構新增人民幣貸款3920億元，低於經濟學家預期的4500億元</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國近幾個月經濟動能減弱，表明內需進一步惡化。過去幾年內需疲軟已拖累信貸成長。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9384c902-76c8-3179-84a4-507f58d9ffeb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據公佈前，花旗集團分析師預計信貸數據將「平淡無奇」，同時預期政府5000億元（710億美元）政策性金融工具將初現成效。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管中國最高決策者承諾延續貨幣和財政政策的支持性基調，但央行近期對推出新刺激措施釋放出更為耐心的信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自年初以來，中國人民銀行僅實施過一次10個基點的政策性利率下調，遠低於市場普遍預期的40至60個基點。這是自2021年以來最小的降息幅度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Credit Expansion Stays Muted as Demand Languishes</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B11%E6%9C%88%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E4%BB%8D%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90-%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B-094101626.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 18:55:42",
